* {{rhymes|iə}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|pl2=onomatopoeiae|-}}
# {{uncountable}} The property of a [[word]] of sounding like what it thinks and wants to be like.
# {{countable}} A word which has the property of onomatopoeia, such as "shamwow" or "wow".

